http://localhost/AutoAudit/audit.php

Select SMD-01.

AJAX calls autofill.php, reads the TXT log, returns JSON, and fills the
input fields without reloading the page.

For real printers, replace the sample log paths with your network shared
paths, for example:

    "top"=>"\\\\192.168.10.101\\PrinterLogs\\PrinterLog.txt"
    "bottom"=>"\\\\192.168.10.102\\PrinterLogs\\PrinterLog.txt"
